id=silence-shutter-screenshot
name=Silence Shutter and Screenshot
version=2.0
versionCode=2
author=hritwik
description=Silences the camera shutter (and screenshot where it is still a loose file) by overlaying a short silent clip over the UI sound files across all partitions (system, product, system_ext, vendor, odm). Fixes the empty-file approach that broke on modern Pixel builds. Note: on Android 13+ the screenshot sound may be baked into SystemUI and unsilenceable by overlay; locked JP/KR regions enforce the shutter below this layer.
